                <footnote.body>
                    <para>
                        <bop/>
                        <bos/>
                        <paratext>Purchaser breached real-estate contract by failing to have funds available to close. Ge Lin v. Ecclestone Signature Homes of Palm Beach,(section 1:4 footnote on page 23)<page no="23"/>LLC, 59 So. 3d 267, 74 U.C.C. Rep. Serv. 2d 293 (Fla. Dist. Ct. App. 4th Dist. 2011). (section 1:4 footnote on page 24)
